{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01GLMBTvCai1Mm14qwvQxXhp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear: `orao-solana-vrf` has `default = [\"sdk\"]`, and we're using `features = [\"cpi\"]` which adds the CPI feature on TOP of the defaults. This means `sdk` is still enabled by default, pulling in `anchor-client`, `solana-rpc-client`, etc.\n\nI need to disable default features and only enable `cpi`:\n\n```toml\norao-solana-vrf = { version = \"0.7.0\", default-features = false, features = [\"cpi\"] }\n```\n\nThis will only enable `cpi` (and its dependency `no-entrypoint`), without the `sdk` feature and its heavy dependencies.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":448,"cache_read_input_tokens":84584,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":448},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"34433cb1-6ee0-432f-833f-aec143a4b7e1","uuid":"eb1fc9eb-7777-41e9-b935-fcfb2b06a50a"}
